<i>noun</i>: 벌점 [벌쩜], 단점 [단ː쩜] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>벌점 [벌쩜]</dt><br>
<dd>1. penalty; demerit</dd><br>
<dd>잘못한 것의 횟수나 정도에 대하여 벌로 따지는 점수.</dd><br>
<dd>Penalty points indicating the number or extent of wrongdoing.</dd><br>
<dd>2. penalty</dd><br>
<dd>얻은 점수 전체에서 벌로 빼는 점수.</dd><br>
<dd>Points taken away from the entire score as a penalty.</dd><br>
<dt>단점 [단ː쩜]</dt><br>
<dd>weakness; shortcoming; demerit</dd><br>
<dd>모자라거나 흠이 되는 점.</dd><br>
<dd>A trait of one's personality that is defective or not admirable.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>